title: The One Where Queen B Rules & Feedback Is King
description:
Lala asked, and you answered! What do you want to hear on the podcast?? Jess reads the feedback that you guys were nice enough to DM, and keeps tally on what you love and what you don’t. And if you listen closely you’ll hear a little “Juicy Scoop” (we love you Heather McDonald) about #PumpRules filming, a special upcoming guest booking, an update on Ocean, Lala’s 5-star review of Queen B’s new album, and another story from Lala’s childhood involving her mom, her brother, and her grandpa Bob!
Learn more about your ad choices. Visit podcastchoices.com/adchoices
